      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nIt's a gcc extension that's been supported almost forever.\nhttps://gcc.gnu.org/onlinedocs/gcc/Pointer-Arith.html\n\nclang and icc support that too.\n\nIt's much cleaner that way, else you have to add 2 cast, from void to char, then back from char to void.",
